snippet.title: Block Smash: Classic Puzzle Game | Gameplay Trailer | Pixeltub Games
snippet.description:
Block Smash Puzzle is a simple free block puzzle game. Very fun to play the Tetris game which is very addictive. This block puzzle game will never let you feel bored! Feel relaxed and train your brain by solving simple puzzles.

This is the gameplay trailer of the new update of this game.
